name: Is this a "Aubergine" or "Au(burge)ne" Combo?
description: Our first different creation! We made an aubergine (eggplant!) meal! So we have two types of sandwitchs: one with bread, grilled eggplants, tomatoes onion and ranch sauce; one with grilled eggplants as bread, chuckpea burger, tomatoes, onions and pickles. With coke, onion rings, and a sweet slice of Red Velvet with chocolate cake!Note: HLE= "Happiness level after eat it"
